    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>You imbue a creature you touch with positive energy to undo a debilitating effect. You can reduce the target's &amp;Reference[exhaustion]{exhaustion} level by one, or end one of the following effects on the target:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>One effect that &amp;Reference[charmed]{charmed} or &amp;Reference[petrified]{petrified} the target</li>\n<li>One curse, including the target's attunement to a cursed magic item</li>\n<li>Any reduction to one of the target's ability scores</li>\n<li>One effect reducing the target's hit point maximum</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
